{
  "stem": "1496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Actually, as far as I know, was the kapos, the Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Schindler, I'm pretty sure-- there must be some kind of list of names from Schindler's factory.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "However, the, the final list was drawn up in Krakau-Plaszow by some of the Jewish police with some of the people who actually were very close to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't know the name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wouldn't want to use any names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were some people were very close working-- those, those are the people who would actually help him to, to get this factory-- the enamel pots and pans factory-- and were advisors to him-- how to handle things.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very short time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say only a few days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because they were-- the Nazis were in a hurry to get as much, as much as possible-- get as many people, also, as possible-- to get out from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, I was much shorter because I spent some time still in the factory where we disassembled the machinery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other people-- most of the people-- they're much longer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were assigned to disassemble some of the barrack, to open up the mass graves because the Nazis wanted to eliminate all of the evidence.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So what they did-- they opened up the mass graves where the people were buried.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For some of them, recently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of them, for two or three years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were carrying the remains on a, on a certain spot where they put wood, and the, the remains were poured-- they, they were pouring gasoline over the remains, and they were burning to ashes.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't want to leave any evidence of what was going-- or as little as possible-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
